      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sure, the white stripe and red fender hash marks are cool, but the real star of the show was that beautiful Admiral Blue paint. It's a particularly vibrant shade of blue, and in the right lighting conditions, it almost has a purple glow to it.",
